node.text:
As witches, many of us work with the energies of the moon, but what about working with the energy of the sun? 🌞 The power of the sun can be harnessed and used in your craft too.

Like you would make Moon water, you can make sun water. Leave water on a sunny windowsill or outside, preferably in direct sunlight, leaving it there from sunrise to sunset.

Sun water can be used is many ways. You can drink it, use it in you bath or in spells and rituals. It’s associated with strength, power, healing, prosperity, confidence, growth and happiness.

Do you use sun water? ☀️💦

Lindsay 💜

✨ P𝕣𝕒𝕔𝕥𝕚𝕔𝕒𝕝 W𝕚𝕥𝕔𝕙𝕔𝕣𝕒𝕗𝕥 T𝕚𝕡𝕤✨
Here’s a collection of hand Witchcraft tips. 

To make black salt with incense ashes, simply add salt to the ashes and to make it black you can use a broken up charcoal disk or the black scrapings from your cauldron.

If you are just starting your Witchcraft journey, don’t think a Witch has to cast a set number of spells each day/week/month. In this sense there are no rules.

Have you got any tried and tested tips?

Lindsay 💜

node.text:
✨ 𝕄𝕠𝕟𝕕𝕒𝕪 𝕥𝕒𝕣𝕠𝕥 𝕣𝕖𝕧𝕖𝕒𝕝!✨
1. The reversed Nine of Wands can indicate that you’re struggling to keep on track as you work towards your goal. You’re not quite ready to give up but you have faced setbacks that have left you wondering if this is the right path. This card is here as reassurance to keep going. It is the right path but first you need to draw upon your inner resources. You are more resilient than you know and you have everything within you to keep on moving forward and achieve you goals. You often speak in a negative manner to yourself and the reversed Nine of Wands asks you challenge any kind of negativity in your mindset and start actively engaging with positive self talk.

2. The Queen of Swords suggests it’s time to lead from the head and not from the heart at the moment. You need to set out clear boundaries so others know what is and what isn’t acceptable. Boundaries are there to protect yourself and often the only people who take some offence to you setting boundaries are the people who benefited from you having non. Be firm and clear because sometimes people take advantage of your kindness and by listening to your head, you are better placed to do so without the influence of emotion. Feelings can often cloud your awareness and understanding of your environment and the people around you. 

3.Temperance is a call to bring more balance into your life and to stabile your energy. If you’ve been feeling out of alignment with certain aspects of your life, it’s time to let the energy flow without being forced or resisted. Letting go of the things you’ve been holding on to lately will allow this energy to flow. It will help you recover your own flow too and with it all comes a greater sense of balance and control. 

Deck: The Modern Way Tarot Deck by the lovely 
@modernwaytarot ✨🔮

✨P𝕤𝕪𝕔𝕙𝕚𝕔 A𝕓𝕚𝕝𝕚𝕥𝕚𝕖𝕤✨
Correspondences are useful when practicing magick as they are collections of different ingredients like crystals or herbs that all have similar magickal qualities and energy. They also include times like days of the week that are also aligned to certain kinds of magick. Correspondences are useful when you know what kind of magick you want to do, but might not know the kinds of ingredients to use. 

These are some correspondence for working with your own psychic abilities. This list isn’t complete, and as your practice, you might create you own list of herbs, crystals and incenses etc that you find works well when working on developing your psychic abilities.

You can use them in spells and rituals to help you connect with and increase your own psychic skills. It can be be something as simple as lighting a purple candle or burning a frankincense incense stick as your magick doesn’t have to be complicated to be effective. 

In terms of timing, Monday is the best day for this kind of magick.

From left to right: crystals, flowers, herbs, planets, colours, tarot cards, day of the week and incense fragrances. 

What are your go to herbs and crystals when you want to connect to your psychic abilities?

Lindsay 💜
